or if it's really this good.

155
00:14:40,422 --> 00:14:42,299
- It's really this good.
- It is, right?

156
00:14:44,468 --> 00:14:46,595
Oh, yeah. Hey, well...

157
00:14:48,305 --> 00:14:51,225
You didn't say, did you
find this world's Amanda?

158
00:14:52,976 --> 00:14:54,686
